absolutely behind durable goods i i think they did a fabulous job i think it's a beautiful looking dust jacket they were really behind it they were very excited about it um i felt great about about everything they did with durable goods so and i went on a little tour and everything and uh so then and then you know it's just been it's just been uh and that now we can kind of get into the books uh that was

