talks as soulful and searching as that.

41:02.606 --> 41:04.670
And it was one of my regrets, in fact.

41:05.010 --> 41:09.479
Also, my friend who died of cancer did not accept the fact that she was going to die.

41:09.499 --> 41:15.310
