and and i have i do have a lot of optimism but i also have you know i also have days that i'm not so optimistic and if i were you know i'd like to be like laney i'd like to be that um continually delighted she is absolutely delighted in small ways all the time and and and i have that but i also feel like you know steamroller comes by every now and then and

