that he doesn't have any legs but he's in the sunshine in his little half cut and he says thank you and he gets a quarter and I don't know and I wanted to be able to do something that would make someone else feel what I felt for that man and range of motion I think of anything I've ever written and there are two that I've written subsequent to that by the way so of the five

